            <lg xml:id="TK939">
<l>uṭaicelva mūṇoḷi kalviyeṉ ṟaintu</l>
<l>maṭaiyāvā māyaṅ koḷiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The habit of gambling prevents the attainment of these five: clothing, wealth, food, fame and learning.</l>
